title>哈马斯拒绝最新提议；部分以色列代表团仍留在卡塔尔</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/hamas-rejects-latest-proposal-in-hostage-negotiations-haniyeh-to-travel-to-iran/0000018e-79ad-dac2-a3de-7dbfa3cb0000</link><description>哈马斯告知调解国家，它坚持两周前提出的立场：全面停火，流离失所的加沙人返回加沙北部，并进行大量囚犯交换以换取释放人质</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 08:16:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/hamas-rejects-latest-proposal-in-hostage-negotiations-haniyeh-to-travel-to-iran/0000018e-79ad-dac2-a3de-7dbfa3cb0000</guid></item><item><title>国防官员担心：比比-拜登的口角可能对美以关系造成持久损害</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/defense-officials-fear-bibi-biden-spat-could-do-lasting-harm-to-u-s-israel-ties/0000018e-7743-dac2-a3de-7ffb86f90000</link><description>以色列总理的威胁没有给美国总统留下任何印象——他已经失去了耐心。美国人不明白内塔尼亚胡想要什么，但从以色列的角度来看，答案很明确：不惜一切代价保住权力</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 04:00:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/defense-officials-fear-bibi-biden-spat-could-do-lasting-harm-to-u-s-israel-ties/0000018e-7743-dac2-a3de-7ffb86f90000</guid></item><item><title>第二个巴勒斯坦难民问题的诞生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/the-birth-of-a-second-palestinian-refugee-problem/0000018e-7660-d680-a1cf-fe67d0770000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡现在必须决定是否将以色列人质带回家并允许加沙北部居民返回——即使以他的执政联盟出现裂痕为代价——还是加入极右翼并宣布创建“巴勒斯坦难民”问题2&amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 04:00:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/the-birth-of-a-second-palestinian-refugee-problem/0000018e-7660-d680-a1cf-fe67d0770000</guid></item><item><title>“协议尚未破裂”：部分以色列代表团仍留在卡塔尔进行人质释放谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article-live/hamas-tells-mediators-it-will-stick-to-original-position-in-cease-fire-talks-with-israel/0000018e-78b4-d8a5-addf-78b7e61c0000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，已发现向以色列北部梅隆空中监视基地发射的火箭弹 ■ 拉法的报道：袭击住宅的袭击造成 18 人死亡，其中一半是儿童 ■ 哈马斯领导人哈尼亚将前往德黑兰与伊朗官员会面 ■ 布林肯敦促加兰特考虑拉法主要地面行动的替代方案 ■ 英国向加沙空投 10 吨食品</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 03:10:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article-live/hamas-tells-mediators-it-will-stick-to-original-position-in-cease-fire-talks-with-israel/0000018e-78b4-d8a5-addf-78b7e61c0000</guid></item><item><title>庆祝活动和抗议活动成为耶路撒冷普珥节游行的焦点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-25/ty-article/.premium/celebrations-protests-take-center-stage-at-jerusalems-purim-parade/0000018e-776d-d8a5-addf-77ff327d0000</link><description>“我们正在使战争正常化。世界将如何看待这一点，”抗议者尼尔·阿尔戈夫说。 “十五万名撤离者无法盛装打扮或庆祝，首都却举办一场盛大的聚会”</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 21:53:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-25/ty-article/.premium/celebrations-protests-take-center-stage-at-jerusalems-purim-parade/0000018e-776d-d8a5-addf-77ff327d0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡不将吉迪恩·萨尔纳入战时内阁后，吉迪恩·萨尔退出联盟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-25/ty-article/.premium/gideon-saar-quits-coalition-after-netanyahu-doesnt-include-him-in-war-cabinet/0000018e-7745-d8a5-addf-77f7264f0000</link><description>萨尔说，他在安全内阁中多次表达了这些观点，但没有效果，因为该论坛已成为一个空谈场所，所有重要决定都是由战时内阁做出的</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 20:47:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-25/ty-article/.premium/gideon-saar-quits-coalition-after-netanyahu-doesnt-include-him-in-war-cabinet/0000018e-7745-d8a5-addf-77f7264f0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡让以色列走上了与美国发生冲突的道路。联合国停火投票是可怕的结果</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-put-israel-on-a-collision-course-with-america-the-un-vote-is-the-result/0000018e-76eb-d616-a7ee-feeb520a0000</link><description>自去年11月以来，我们多次撰文表示这种情况将会发生，美国也不断警告以色列这种情况很可能发生。以色列无视这些威胁，现在不诚实地假装惊讶和震惊</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 19:49:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-put-israel-on-a-collision-course-with-america-the-un-vote-is-the-result/0000018e-76eb-d616-a7ee-feeb520a0000</guid></item><item><title>这位非犹太同性恋喜剧演员如何成为以色列最热情的倡导者之一</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-03-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-this-non-jewish-gay-comedian-became-one-of-israels-most-passionate-advocates/0000018e-762b-d96c-af9f-7eeb69a80000</link><description>过去，出生于加拿大的丹尼尔-瑞安·斯波尔丁甚至不确定自己在以色列表演是否舒服。自 10 月 7 日袭击以来，他已成为网上最知名的以色列捍卫者和哈马斯攻击者之一。但甚至不要让他开始柏林</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 19:02:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-03-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-this-non-jewish-gay-comedian-became-one-of-israels-most-passionate-advocates/0000018e-762b-d96c-af9f-7eeb69a80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 171 天：美国称以色列遵守国家安全备忘录</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-25/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-171-u-s-says-israel-complying-with-national-security-memorandum/0000018e-76ac-d8a5-addf-76bfb9230001</link><description>联合国安理会通过决议，呼吁加沙立即停火，在美国弃权后释放所有人质 ■ 作为回应，内塔尼亚胡总理取消了前往华盛顿的代表团，该代表团旨在讨论在拉法攻势中保护平民的努力 ■ 以色列国防军表示已结束在哈马德的行动汗尤尼斯 (Khan Yunis) 社区 ■ 战争开始 171 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 17:49:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-25/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-171-u-s-says-israel-complying-with-national-security-memorandum/0000018e-76ac-d8a5-addf-76bfb9230001</guid></item><item><title>特朗普警告以色列：“你正在失去很多世界，你正在失去很多支持”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-25/ty-article/.premium/trump-warns-israel-youre-losing-a-lot-of-the-world-youre-losing-a-lot-of-support/0000018e-7685-d680-a1cf-fe8728e90000</link><description>美国前总统多兰·特朗普在接受Israel Hayom采访时将哈马斯10月7日对美国总统乔·拜登的袭击归咎于哈马斯，称这是因为哈马斯“不尊重他”，并补充说“他们（哈马斯）永远不会”如果我在的话，就会发动那次袭击。”</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 17:24:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-25/ty-article/.premium/trump-warns-israel-youre-losing-a-lot-of-the-world-youre-losing-a-lot-of-support/0000018e-7685-d680-a1cf-fe8728e90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方调查特拉维夫性俱乐部强奸案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-investigate-rape-at-tel-aviv-sex-clubs/0000018e-761c-dfa8-a7de-f63f3fd60000</link><description>特拉维夫南部由著名夜生活人物 Nissan Gavni 经营的两个地点涉嫌被用作未经同意的身体虐待和性虐待场所。</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 16:20:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-investigate-rape-at-tel-aviv-sex-clubs/0000018e-761c-dfa8-a7de-f63f3fd60000</guid></item><item><title>在对乌克兰问题保持沉默后，以色列对莫斯科恐怖袭击的反应充满了幸灾乐祸的味道</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-25/ty-article/.premium/after-silence-on-ukraine-israeli-reactions-to-moscow-terror-attack-reek-of-schadenfreude/0000018e-75fd-d189-a7be-f5fddc390000</link><description>是的，存在着激进的伊斯兰恐怖主义，其行动范围是全球性的，而且它不歧视以色列人、俄罗斯人、美国人或阿富汗人。但以色列政界人士应该更清楚地将俄罗斯袭击事件与 10 月 7 日联系起来</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 16:12:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-25/ty-article/.premium/after-silence-on-ukraine-israeli-reactions-to-moscow-terror-attack-reek-of-schadenfreude/0000018e-75fd-d189-a7be-f5fddc390000</guid></item><item><title>以色列考古学家确定了人类进化的“神圣三位一体”：水、石头和大象</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-03-25/ty-article/archaeologists-identify-holy-triad-of-human-evolution-water-stone-and-elephants/0000018e-75ff-d680-a1cf-ffff632f0000</link><description>数千年来，以色列的早期人类进行了漫长而艰苦的跋涉，从特定的采石场获取制作工具的理想石头。为什么？</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 16:09:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-03-25/ty-article/archaeologists-identify-holy-triad-of-human-evolution-water-stone-and-elephants/0000018e-75ff-d680-a1cf-ffff632f0000</guid></item><item><title>在美国投弃权票要求加沙停火的联合国决议后，内塔尼亚胡取消了华盛顿代表团</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-cancels-washington-delegation-after-u-s-abstains-from-un-gaza-cease-fire-vote/0000018e-7622-d96c-af9f-7ee3aeb80000</link><description>联合国安理会决议要求加沙停火，这是自战争爆发以来美国放弃使用否决权后首次通过决议，尽管内塔尼亚胡威胁要取消华盛顿对拉法的代表团</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 15:45:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-cancels-washington-delegation-after-u-s-abstains-from-un-gaza-cease-fire-vote/0000018e-7622-d96c-af9f-7ee3aeb80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长表示，正统派军队豁免法缺乏实质内容；联盟提交新版本</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-25/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-haredi-army-exemption-law-is-lacks-substance-govt-working-on-new-version/0000018e-7515-df29-a7ee-77d53d5b0000</link><description>在内塔尼亚胡政府试图继续豁免极端正统派入伍的争议中，总检察长办公室告诉总理，如果没有提出新的内阁决议，犹太学院的学生将被征召入伍。 ■ 联盟同意放弃将豁免年龄提高到 35 岁</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 11:20:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-25/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-haredi-army-exemption-law-is-lacks-substance-govt-working-on-new-version/0000018e-7515-df29-a7ee-77d53d5b0000</guid></item><item><title>斯莫特里奇方法：以色列定居者获得抵押贷款，在西岸其他地方非法建造</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-smotrich-scheme-israeli-settlers-obtain-mortgages-build-illegally-in-the-west-bank/0000018e-7107-d1c9-af8f-7fafa6060000</link><description>以色列极右翼财政部长的一名助手获得了一个定居点分区计划中登记的土地的抵押贷款，而他的家建在附近的一个非法前哨基地。文件和航拍照片表明他远非唯一一个</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 10:42:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-smotrich-scheme-israeli-settlers-obtain-mortgages-build-illegally-in-the-west-bank/0000018e-7107-d1c9-af8f-7fafa6060000</guid></item><item><title>“感觉受到威胁”：以色列在没有批评或监督的情况下杀人的处方</title><link>https://www.haaretz.